description:
This is a 35 minute workout called '30 MIN PILATES WORKOUT || Mat Pilates With Weights (Intermediate)' from the channel Move With Nicole.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates and Cardio/Mat.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Weights for this workout.
The workout has a The Masterclass Workout and The Rhythmic Powerhouse vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Challenging.

Original workout description: This 30 Minute Mat Pilates class works the entire body but with a special focus on strengthening the core. I recommend using 1kg-2kg weights but don't worry if you don't have weights as you can still enjoy the class without them. You could also be creative and use household objects like cans of beans or bottles of water to act as weights! I hope you enjoy it. üòä
